{"tid":2493962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 消防於飛鵝山發現一名昏迷人士 懷疑是失蹤的石樂蕎","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T10:42:36.000Z","uid":147376,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb32260e584e72911323add08414120510c490b","tid":2493962,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Heiheihits/videos/316447546572270/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHeiheihits%2Fvideos%2F316447546572270%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=c62c63be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Heiheihits/videos/316447546572270/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n‼️ALERT  飛鵝山突發 持續更新‼️<br />\n<br />\n1755：據01報導，消防尋找到一個昏迷人士，正是失蹤者，正安排直升機運送傷者<br />\n<br />\n1751：有消息指有直升機降落於灣仔金紫荊廣場<br />\n<br />\n1747：飛行服務隊直升機離開飛鵝山現場<br />\n<br />\n1744：有現場消息指警員曾於下午五時左右表示「有發現」<br />\n<br />\n1743：‼️有待確認‼️有消息指事主正在下山<br />\n<br />\n1736：有人係社交媒體拍到民安隊搜救情況，疑似係拯救懷疑失蹤者。<br />\n<br />\n1732：東區醫院停機坪有救護人員準備<br />\n<br />\n1730：1消防裝備車由飛鵝山1號駛入封鎖線內<br />\n有多名消防員落地準備上山<br />\n<br />\n1726:‼️有待證實‼️🚨有消息指民安隊有擔架床於自殺崖山壁中被直升機吊起"},{"pid":"6533993f0aa1645160c3a2bcfab70e781492b90a","tid":2493962,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0be7019228622f570d48eb1c0f953501ea8aea84","tid":2493962,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b916e7f9cc1fcbabcdd9f488e69b443f36f5be1","tid":2493962,"uid":26329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"好彩今日天氣涼，仲有得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b33c1aa57bdb705eb45bebe9101c7a04270ce62","tid":2493962,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"希望冇事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf